text: Artonges is a former commune. It is in the Hauts-de-France region in the Aisne department in the north of France. In 2012, 194 people lived there. On 1 January 2016, it was merged into the new commune Dhuys-et-Morin-en-Brie.Arrêté préfectoral 10 September 2015 ==References== Category:Former communes in Aisne
title: Artonges
